no hands’? "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or making? Your work has no hands."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 29:16","book":"Isa","chapter":29,"verse":16},{"label":"Is 64:8","book":"Isa","chapter":64,"verse":8},{"label":"Jr 18:6","book":"Jer","chapter":18,"verse":6},{"label":"Rm 9:20–21","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit a clay pot with clay pots of the ground"},{"marker":1,"text":"Or making? Your work has no hands."}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:45:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Woe to the one who says to his father,"},{"kind":"text","text":" ‘What are you fathering?’"},{"kind":"text","text":" or to his mother, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit to a woman"},{"kind":"text","text":" ‘What are you giving birth to?’”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit to a woman"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:45:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This is what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"text","text":" the Holy One of Israel "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 1:4","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and its Maker, says:"},{"kind":"text","text":" “Ask me what is to happen to "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or me the coming things about"},{"kind":"text","text":" my sons, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 31:9","book":"Jer","chapter":31,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and instruct me about the work of my hands. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 19:25","book":"Isa","chapter":19,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 29:23","book":"Isa","chapter":29,"verse":23,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 60:21","book":"Isa","chapter":60,"verse":21,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 64:8","book":"Isa","chapter":64,"verse":8,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 1:4","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":4},{"label":"Jr 31:9","book":"Jer","chapter"